{
  "stem": "22869.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were there received by [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Hlinka guard, which is the equivalent on the SS guard in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Black uniforms, wild dogs, rifles, hittings over the head and yelling and screaming, the dogs barking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They drove into you a fear that you knew this is it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now if we had a chance, of course, to turn around, we would've gladly done it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that chance was taken away the minute we saw their-- and-- and-- all our-- we were all young people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would say maybe my uncle was maybe-- was maybe 35, maybe even younger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, all these really young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We realized right away that things are not good, that this is-- this is-- this is it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, they were starting beating that we never saw in our life-- really subhuman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and we knew that something awful is-- is awaiting us, at this point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The last time I saw my mother, when she came to bring some food to the place, to this first gathering place I mentioned to you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, since we thought we were parting, you know, for a couple of months maybe, you know, she was crying, and we hugged.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly the words we said to each other, but it-- it wasn't kind of an emotional good-bye-saying as we would have said if that would have happened in Zilina a day later, because when we know that this is-- they mean business now.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Zilina, we were there, I think, about 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave us some packages of food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
